kainga
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a dwelling; an unfortified place of residence; an unfortified village'; North island equivalent of "kaika"
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also kaik(a)
Pronunciation:
